column2: SELECT m.id, n.objid, n.distance, o.petroMag_u-o.extinction_u as u_pmag, o.petroMag_g-o.extinction_g as g_pmag, o.petroMag_r-o.extinction_r as r_pmag, o.petroMag_i-o.extinction_i as i_pmag, o.petroMag_z-o.extinction_z as z_pmag, E_bv = extinction_r/# FROM MyDB.temp AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid JOIN Photoz as h on h.objid = o.objid order by id
